title: GoPro: Still Lost in Peru
description:
Shot 100% on the HD HERO3+® camera from http://GoPro.com.

Aaron Chase gets lost in Peru again with Chris Van Dine, Ali Goulet, Katie Holden and Rich Van Every.

Music
Oli Denney "Star Gazer" & "What Are You Going To Do"

Quantic Soul Orchestra "Terrapin"


Wildlife "Bonnie"


Additional Music Courtesy of ExtremeMusic
